#: ../../D/defenestration.rst:5
msgid "defenestration"
msgstr "defenestration"

#: ../../D/defenestration.rst:7
msgid "n\\."
msgstr "名詞"

#: ../../D/defenestration.rst:9
msgid ""
"[mythically from a traditional Bohemian assassination method, via SF fandom]"
msgstr "[SFファンダムを経由した、伝説的にはボヘミアの伝統的な暗殺方法から]"

#: ../../D/defenestration.rst:12
msgid ""
"Proper karmic retribution for an incorrigible punster. \"Oh, ghod, that was "
"awful!\" \"Quick! Defenestrate him!\""
msgstr ""
"矯正不能な駄洒落屋に対する適切なカルマ的報い。「ああ、なんてひどい駄洒落だ!」「早く! あいつをdefenestrateしろ(窓から放り出せ)!」"

#: ../../D/defenestration.rst:18
msgid ""
"The act of completely removing Micro$oft Windows from a PC in favor of a "
"better OS (typically Linux)."
msgstr "より良いOS(通常はLinux)のために、PCからMicro$oft Windowsを完全に取り除く行為。"

#: ../../D/defenestration.rst:21
msgid ""
"The act of discarding something under the assumption that it will improve "
"matters. \"I don't have any disk space left.\" \"Well, why don't you "
"defenestrate that 100 megs worth of old core dumps?\""
msgstr ""
"事態を改善するだろうという想定のもとに、何かを捨てる行為。「ディスク容量がもう残っていないんだ。」「じゃあ、その100メガ分の古いコアダンプをdefenestrateしたらどうだ?」"

#: ../../D/defenestration.rst:26
msgid ""
"Under a GUI, the act of dragging something out of a window (onto the "
"screen). \"Next, defenestrate the MugWump icon.\""
msgstr "GUIのもとで、何かをウィンドウから(画面上へ)ドラッグして引き出す行為。「次に、MugWumpアイコンをdefenestrateせよ。」"

#: ../../D/defenestration.rst:30
msgid ""
"[obs.] The act of exiting a window system in order to get better response "
"time from a full-screen program. This comes from the dictionary meaning of "
"defenestrate, which is to throw something out a window."
msgstr ""
"[廃語] "
"フルスクリーンのプログラムからより良い応答時間を得るために、ウィンドウシステムを終了する行為。これはdefenestrateの辞書的な意味、すなわち何かを窓から放り投げることに由来する。"
